title: EYL #160 Millionaire Mindset feat. TJ Millionaire Mentor
itunes:title: EYL #160 Millionaire Mindset feat. TJ Millionaire Mentor
description:
On episode #160, we spoke with multi millionaire entrepreneur Todd Johnson aka TJ Millionaire Mentor. Todd walked us through his business journey and the steps he took to become successful. 


This is a powerful high level conversation about business creation, selling a business for eight figures, the ups and downs of entrepreneurship, online marketing, and more. #TJMillionaireMentor #business #earnyourleisure
